  <li>8:09 Riff 1 of 6</li>
  <li>11:10 Riff 2 of 6</li>
  <li>13:57 Riff 3 of 6</li>
  <li>15:25 Riff 4 of 6</li>
  <li>17:03 Riff 5 of 6</li>
  <li>18:01 Riff 6 of 6</li>
  <li>19:41 Farewell &amp; final advice</li>
