B ––1––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––|––––––
G ––2–––––––––––––––2–0–––––––––0––––|––––––
D ––2–––––––––––––––––––––––0–2––––––|––––––
A ––0––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––|––––––
